context-engineered DQ rule authoring platform.

The goal is:

user selects a dataset
system loads the prejoined SQL / JSON-SQL path
system resolves all physical attributes in scope
system enriches with catalog metadata
user writes an English rule
LLM converts it into validated AWS Deequ rule JSON/expression
system stores, versions, and executes it safely

So the LLM is not discovering the enterprise blindly.
It is operating inside a strict boundary created by:

dataset selection
parsed prejoined SQL
scoped attributes
metadata enrichment
rule template library
validation gates




